{"tid":987091,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"半年前遊捷匈斯，依家先開","createTime":"2019-01-19T04:42:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-07T16:48:28.000Z","uid":147499,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"03a3c9115c18e1aae4c885a4fb6051a5060910b3","tid":987091,"uid":147499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T04:42:32.000Z","msg":"半年前暑假，同男朋友兩丁友去歐洲<br />\n本身打算去巴爾幹<br />\n但因為機票太貴，同埋要轉兩次機，所以作罷<br />\n最後搵到六千幾蚊飛布拉格，中間杜拜轉機<br />\n所以決定去捷克、匈牙利同斯洛伐克<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為真係有d耐，好多記憶都開始模糊<br />\n不過又覺得呢趟旅程幾值得記低<br />\n所以順便開post同大家分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一開始，送張布拉格藝術館俾大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WdusBJC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWdusBJC.png&h=0967344f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後等我慢慢打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89c155f06550612aa4e5839485c81ce2df25271d","tid":987091,"uid":147499,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T04:55:34.000Z","msg":"8月1號晚上出發去機場，搭阿聯猶凌晨機<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xnqfLDc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxnqfLDc.png&h=5b1244c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n窮L搭經濟艙，真心窄<br />\n訓下醒下咁，啪左甜睡寧都俾d光整醒左<br />\n<br />\n大概點幾，空姐派左個好鹹嘅雞肉火腿包<br />\n逼自己食dd再訓<br />\n<br />\n若是這般，八小時之後，兩條喪屍到左杜拜<br />\n<br />\n竟然有雪糕派<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VNMe1bz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVNMe1bz.png&h=f7fae0ee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WZ2Fcie.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWZ2Fcie.png&h=cdc4d1a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食完又周圍望下<br />\n落地玻璃上面嘅花紋幾靚<br />\n等左六個鐘轉機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H2YUgKV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH2YUgKV.png&h=6968640c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n終於開始第二程，打下機、睇下嘉玲姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BPUDJpW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBPUDJpW.png&h=65ef51f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ssVvzwC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FssVvzwC.png&h=ae79230d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中間會飛越伊朗上空<br />\n阿聯猶可以上網20分鐘，所以即刻check到係邊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GANqopY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGANqopY.png&h=109434c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n頭已側<br />\n其實阿聯猶嘅飛機餐就好食<br />\n不過因為喪屍訓唔到導致冇食欲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YhH9P4Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYhH9P4Z.png&h=9ee9cd27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n18個鐘之後終於到布拉格<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當地時間下午四點幾，香港時間早上十點幾<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4PaO5Dk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4PaO5Dk.png&h=e5b12acc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"93729dc05ba19b29384140b32928bb861ff86199","tid":987091,"uid":128271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T04:57:38.000Z","msg":"lm 想去布拉格"},{"pid":"2f31745bc34707b0915dd97d66fdacae3fc4d1b9","tid":987091,"uid":20468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T05:26:26.000Z","msg":"個士多啤梨mousse好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都係差唔多半年前去咗東歐grad trip 好懷念"},{"pid":"42c5be4348bcf2cc714cfce7feaec52f1c04638b","tid":987091,"uid":147499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T05:48:56.000Z","msg":"電話卡係香港買左，一張3uk，1張wechat<br />\n至於布拉格嘅交通都幾正<br />\n佢唔係按距離收費，而係按時間收費<br />\n係時限之內可以無限搭<br />\n可以選擇買30分鐘、60分鐘、24小時、72小時<br />\n至於當地人，我估就有月票啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iGyJanN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiGyJanN.png&h=d1c144f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n310捷克幣大概等於百幾港紙，咁可以搭72小時<br />\n最特別嘅係，佢地無論tram定地鐵<br />\n都係自出自入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除非係第一次入閘先要放張車飛入閘機<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於攜帶大型行李，梗係要搭升降機啦<br />\n不過見到個0字都再次感受到culture shock<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aaCRjf8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaaCRjf8.png&h=322ff4f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n布拉格嘅地鐵線路感覺都幾似香港<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xsitmuu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxsitmuu.png&h=77b6e0b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過電梯好長好慢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GOMKEgb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGOMKEgb.png&h=1f500a93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n終於到地面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zxGCePx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzxGCePx.png&h=c1f45f07&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3599d09a77fa8c5f655e9f33369c92231210fc03","tid":987091,"uid":147499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f31745bc34707b0915dd97d66fdacae3fc4d1b9","tid":987091,"uid":20468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T05:26:26.000Z","msg":"個士多啤梨mousse好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都係差唔多半年前去咗東歐grad trip 好懷念"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T05:50:44.000Z","msg":"朱古力都好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05ab0280a1f47ffbca37bc1a3234b4c22db868fa","tid":987091,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T08:06:36.000Z","msg":"推 最後去左幾日到？"},{"pid":"df6f7412a0684c7ca6bc72575ab8716615f71e34","tid":987091,"uid":82765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T09:14:02.000Z","msg":"岩岩去完<br />\n多人到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58c705a44613eab2fbfc49dd157eeead0ff53b0a","tid":987091,"uid":147499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05ab0280a1f47ffbca37bc1a3234b4c22db868fa","tid":987091,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T08:06:36.000Z","msg":"推 最後去左幾日到？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T09:29:03.000Z","msg":"18日啊"},{"pid":"01db05dffa69f3a02932feea76c05a3736fe2dec","tid":987091,"uid":147499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df6f7412a0684c7ca6bc72575ab8716615f71e34","tid":987091,"uid":82765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T09:14:02.000Z","msg":"岩岩去完<br />\n多人到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T09:29:13.000Z","msg":"好多大陸人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01b5b81264e362c0d3cb7a97959d2e5c7fdd3c3b","tid":987091,"uid":82765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01db05dffa69f3a02932feea76c05a3736fe2dec","tid":987091,"uid":147499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df6f7412a0684c7ca6bc72575ab8716615f71e34","tid":987091,"uid":82765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T09:14:02.000Z","msg":"岩岩去完<br />\n多人到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T09:29:13.000Z","msg":"好多大陸人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T09:39:07.000Z","msg":"咩人都有唔止強仔<br />\n不過我揸車所以去左其他周邊地方"},{"pid":"4085837f6be9c3febd30d2243c921e4a237e6b9a","tid":987091,"uid":79292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01db05dffa69f3a02932feea76c05a3736fe2dec","tid":987091,"uid":147499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df6f7412a0684c7ca6bc72575ab8716615f71e34","tid":987091,"uid":82765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T09:14:02.000Z","msg":"岩岩去完<br />\n多人到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T09:29:13.000Z","msg":"好多大陸人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T09:39:39.000Z","msg":"好撚多韓妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n靚嘅醜嘅都有"},{"pid":"49ca2298e168d1d0edc4ed73f5321c20e904a6c7","tid":987091,"uid":34095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T10:14:35.000Z","msg":"覺得prague真係被吹大咗 東歐最正都係去啲小鎮"},{"pid":"0705de2977cbc13856bc5c775061378881f94d82","tid":987091,"uid":13514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T10:23:42.000Z","msg":"想知暑假個陣天氣日頭同夜晚溫差大唔大?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就咁著短袖衫短褲夠唔夠?"},{"pid":"450c2d6cf6b01a7681dc2cabec90030bcd2303c5","tid":987091,"uid":147499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T10:58:13.000Z","msg":"因為男朋友之前去旅行識左個捷克女仔<br />\n所以今日一落機，係airbnb放低嘢就去左搵佢<br />\n佢係布拉格做導遊<br />\n所以英文都幾好<br />\n<br />\n跟住好快咁行左新舊城區啊Charles Bridge咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XBriLqT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXBriLqT.png&h=b07a37df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nCharles Bridge最特別係<br />\n佢興建於1357年7月11日5時31分<br />\n而且之後經歷好幾次洪水都冇被沖爛<br />\n所以d人覺得佢有股神奇嘅力量<br />\n導致附近嘅街道全部都係得單數編號<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5LvrUje.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5LvrUje.png&h=43239980&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S10fNEf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS10fNEf.png&h=071cd432&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行到咁上下，捷克朋友就帶左我地去食飯<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EzwbkZg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEzwbkZg.png&h=21ade5b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為佢地冇相機食先嘅習慣<br />\n加上佢仲同我地講<br />\n自己會笑d大陸人影食物<br />\n所以我冇影到當晚食左咩<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ecUTzji.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FecUTzji.png&h=1859cd53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁我就食左dumpling<br />\n個人覺得係厚切嘅巨型饅頭<br />\n仲要點紅酒會牛肉嘅汁<br />\n我唔可以話佢唔好食，但真係好有趣嘅感覺<br />\n<br />\n最後，送上捷克美女嘅背脊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aDgOocF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaDgOocF.png&h=f74f68fc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"18c5402aea2f4c7313b4df2bb110d1fe574bb374","tid":987091,"uid":147499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0705de2977cbc13856bc5c775061378881f94d82","tid":987091,"uid":13514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T10:23:42.000Z","msg":"想知暑假個陣天氣日頭同夜晚溫差大唔大?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就咁著短袖衫短褲夠唔夠?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T11:18:35.000Z","msg":"我覺得ok<br />\n不過8月中開始夜晚都涼"},{"pid":"715ad4fc17ad922a5594ebcc78de0491e7b975ad","tid":987091,"uid":147499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01b5b81264e362c0d3cb7a97959d2e5c7fdd3c3b","tid":987091,"uid":82765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01db05dffa69f3a02932feea76c05a3736fe2dec","tid":987091,"uid":147499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df6f7412a0684c7ca6bc72575ab8716615f71e34","tid":987091,"uid":82765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T09:14:02.000Z","msg":"岩岩去完<br />\n多人到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T09:29:13.000Z","msg":"好多大陸人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T09:39:07.000Z","msg":"咩人都有唔止強仔<br />\n不過我揸車所以去左其他周邊地方"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T11:18:54.000Z","msg":"後來我地都有啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff41f258b422e7ac5e38c66a330d4b4ce0f5b8a2","tid":987091,"uid":24368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T11:29:03.000Z","msg":"我都係暑假去<br />\n熱到癲"},{"pid":"aa64bc19dc8cccd8952fd98fb22179e3aab8f1c3","tid":987091,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T14:01:29.000Z","msg":"專程18日去捷匈<br />\n你地兩個應該好hea<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89774001c13371e942c1b7054aac520d285634e5","tid":987091,"uid":147499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"aa64bc19dc8cccd8952fd98fb22179e3aab8f1c3","tid":987091,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T14:01:29.000Z","msg":"專程18日去捷匈<br />\n你地兩個應該好hea<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <im